THIRD-PARTY DATA — SEPARATE TERMS APPLY (this MIT licence covers only the code)

* Elexon Insights / BMRS data is published under Elexon's open licence. Attribute
  Elexon and comply with https://www.elexon.co.uk/ terms when redistributing data.
* NESO (National Energy System Operator) data portal datasets are published under
  dataset-specific open licences (typically NESO Open Licence / CC-BY). Attribute
  NESO and check each dataset's licence.
* EPEX SPOT order-book data is licensed and MUST NOT be redistributed. This project
  contains no EPEX data and only a stub adapter documenting what a licence requires.

See docs/data_sources.md and docs/limitations.md for full attribution and terms.
